title: [FSX/P3D] Milviz F-4J/S Phantom II v 1.160306 (June 7, 2016)
description:
Here is the latest Milviz F-4J/S triple installer for FSX, FSX-SE, and P3D v. 3.3+   Note: to the best of my knowledge, this will only work specifically on P3D versions 3.3 or higher; the installer is not backwardly compatible with earlier versions of P3D.   

There appears to an issue with the cockpit flap position indicators with the P3D version, but this is par for the course with Milviz's current attitude of 'we'll fix it - maybe, sometime'.    Oh and the flap position indicators have been broken in some form or another for the last six months in previous versions.   So, this is why we pirate them instead of paying.   :)
